ActParliament of Canada Act
SubjectMembers of the House of Commons to be Parliamentary Secretary to the Ministers ** Appointment **
PrecisOrder (1) terminating the appointment of Kevin Lamoureux made by Order in Council P.C. 2019-1374 of November 20, 2019; and (2) appointing, for the period ending on December 10, 2020, certain Members of the House of Commons to be Parliamentary Secretaries to the Ministers.
